videos.headline: Franklin to the house for a TD
videos.description: Jarvion Franklin rumbles 47 yards for the opening touchdown for Western Michigan.

videos.headline: Franklin rumbles for a big gain
videos.description: Jarvion Franklin runs for a 38 yards to put Western Michigan deep in Chippewas territory.

videos.headline: Tucker leads ground attack for TD
videos.description: Davon Tucker 8-yard touchdown run pushes the lead for Western Michigan.

videos.headline: Ward takes pass for big gain
videos.description: Jonathan Ward takes the swing pass 44 yards to set up Central Michigan in Western Michigan terrority.

videos.headline: Morris with a fake and score for TD
videos.description: Shane Morris's play fake and runs 3 yards for a touchdown to put Central Michigan in the game.

videos.headline: Bunting's INT stops Western Michigan's drive
videos.description: Western Michigan's Reece Goddard over throws a pass that is picked off by Central Michigan's Sean Bunting, who returns it 18 yards.

videos.headline: Bogan's run puts Westen Michigan on the doorstep
videos.description: Jamauri Bogan's 20-yard gain sets up the Broncos with a first and goal.

videos.headline: Bogan walks into the endzone
videos.description: Jamauri Bogan goes untouched for a 2-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Morris to Willis puts Central Michigan deep in Western Michigan territory.
videos.description: Shane Morris hits Corey Willis for a 37-yard gain to set up a Chippewas touchdown.

videos.headline: Central Michigan chipping away
videos.description: Shane Morris runs in from eight yards out to cut the Western Michigan lead to 21-14.

videos.headline: Grace's fumble recovery puts Western Michigan in the red zone
videos.description: Alex Grace recovers Mark Chapman's fumble to set up Western Michigan in scoring position.

videos.headline: Franklin muscles in for another Western Michigan TD
videos.description: Jarvion Franklin's second touchdown run pads the lead for the Broncos.

videos.headline: Central Michigan's defense comes through with turnover
videos.description: Caleb Bailey's fumble recovery off bad snap give new life to Central Michigan down 28-14.

videos.headline: Franklin fumble keeps Central Michigan in the game
videos.description: Jarvion Franklin fumbles and it's recovered by Central Michigan in Broncos' territory.

videos.headline: Ward's TD narrows the gap
videos.description: Jonathan Ward's 29-yard touchdown run cuts the Western Michigan lead to 28-21 in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Morris finds Cooper to tie game
videos.description: Shane Morris connects with Eric Cooper from 9 yards out to tie the game 28-28 late in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Morris to Willis gives Central Michigan its first lead
videos.description: Shane Morris hits Corey Willis for a 77-yard touchdown to give the Chippewas its first lead of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_Final Game Highlight Central Michigan (Morris to Willis gives Central Michigan its first lead) 2017/11/02

videos.headline: Last gasp for Western Michigan slips away on 4th down
videos.description: Keishawn Watson drops the ball on 4th down to seal the game for Central Michigan.

videos.headline: Central Michigan's Ward celebrates with the Cannon trophy
videos.description: Jonathan Ward celebrates with the Cannon trophy as Central Michigan beats Western Michigan for the first time in four years.

videos.headline: Bonamgeo emotional after comeback win
videos.description: John Bonamgeo credits his team's heart and guts in their 35-28 comeback win over Western Michigan.

videos.headline: A tale of two halves in Central Michigan's victory over Western Michigan
videos.description: Chris Cotter and Desmond Howard discuss Central Michigan's roller coaster 35-28 win over Western Michigan.
